==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lidless
<hw>Lid"less</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧d"l⟦ecr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having
no lid, or not covered with the lids, as the eyes; hence, sleepless;
watchful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>lidless</qex> watcher of the public weal.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>lido</ent>⟦br⟧
